Requirements:
• Diploma or above in Computer Science or related discipline;
• Proficient in Python, Matlab, Java, C#, C/C++ and SQL;
• Knowledge of CUDA or other GPGPU is a plus;
• Experience using framework such as Tensorflow, Keras, pytorch etc;
• Excellent understanding in computer vision algorithm (both machine learning and image procession);
• Hand on experience in computer vision projects;
• Experience with deep learning frameworks such as Tensorflow or PyTorch is a plus;
• Hardworking well organized and able to work independently under pressure;
• Candidate with less experience will be consider as programmer;
• Fresh graduates are also welcome

